#386  Featuring the first appearance of Black Mask! After losing control of his company, cosmetics king Roman Sionis becomes the criminal known as Black Mask in order to take revenge. Continued in DETECTIVE COMICS (1937-2011) #553. 

#387  Bruce Wayne hosts a masquerade ball at Wayne Manor in hopes of luring the criminal Black Mask into a confrontation. 

#389  With the Crisis turning the skies red, Batman re-encounters Catwoman and Nocturna while the Night-Slayer goes on a killing rampage against the False Face Society. Continued in DETECTIVE COMICS (1937-2011) #556. 

#390  Continued from DETECTIVE COMICS (1937-2011) #556. While Nocturna tries to discover what's causing the red rain, Catwoman battles the Dynamic Duo. Continued in DETECTIVE COMICS (1937-2011) #557.
